metadata.name: 春の花嫁~bride of spring~
metadata.description:
Cherry Blossoms.
Even if it doesn't come true.
I carry my feelings for him on my petals.
Fly as far as you can.
And one day, I will, too.
I'll see you again.

桜よ
たとえ叶わなくても
あの人への想いを花びらに乗せて
どこまでも飛んでゆけ
そうすれば　いつか　私も
またあなたに会えるはず

2198×3519　300dpi
